snippet.title: A Super Mario Thing - 1 - super demo rpg
snippet.description:
Man, I am SO sorry for the commentary quality in this video. I guess I was just... Drinking it all up, you know? 

To be fair, this is basically how I reacted during two of my favourite hacks, both of which my LP runs were actually NOT blind (TSRPR and VIP4). There's some adaption to be had, I reckon.

Also, this is proof that I would be horrible during an rpg lp. May the debate rest!

http://www.raocow.com
